  "detailed_description": "<strong>DESERT KILL</strong> is a roguelite top-down shooter where you have to destroy evil forces in the most brutal way!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912070/extras/a778c47aa058afd78a65e154be8df154.poster.avif?t=1728296775\" width=620 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912070/extras/a778c47aa058afd78a65e154be8df154.webm?t=1728296775\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912070/extras/a778c47aa058afd78a65e154be8df154.mp4?t=1728296775\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The world was stuck in endless wars.  Сonflict of interest led to a global cataclysm and a most of our planet became a lifeless desert.<br><br>Taking advantage of the global chaos, the terrible villain tries to muster his personal army to seize power over the rest of the world.<br><br>The toughest and incredibly dangerous killers splitted in two camps - those who want to save the remnants of our world and those who are eager to seize absolute power!<br><br>Choose your hero and stop the evil!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912070/extras/d9319a859e04743c20c2d2d9d12381f3.poster.avif?t=1728296775\" width=306 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912070/extras/d9319a859e04743c20c2d2d9d12381f3.webm?t=1728296775\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912070/extras/d9319a859e04743c20c2d2d9d12381f3.mp4?t=1728296775\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https:/